---
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>404 | Gromit's Lab</title>
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
    <meta name="description" content="This page doesn't exist. You’ve hit a dead sector..." />
    <style>
      body {
        background-color: #0d0d0d;
        color: #33ff33;
        font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
        padding: 2rem;
        margin: 0;
      }
      .terminal {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 3rem auto;
        padding: 2rem;
        border: 2px solid #33ff33;
        border-radius: 10px;
        background-color: #000;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px #33ff33;
      }
      .terminal h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      .terminal p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin: 0.5rem 0;
      }
      .blink {
        animation: blink 1s infinite;
      }
      @keyframes blink {
        0%   { opacity: 1; }
        50%  { opacity: 0; }
        100% { opacity: 1; }
      }
      a {
        color: #33ff33;
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
      a:hover {
        color: #00ffcc;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main class="terminal">
      <h1>> SYSTEM FAILURE: CODE 404</h1>
      <p>> The page you’re looking for has been wiped… maybe by an APT group.</p>
      <p>> Or maybe Wallace sat on the server again.</p>
      <p>> Try typing <code>cd /</code> to return to safety.</p>
      <p>> <a href="/">Return to Homepage</a> <span class="blink">_</span></p>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
